---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <div class="bg-gray-950 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 prose prose-invert">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Should You Build Your Own Gaming PC in 2026?</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">July 2026 • RigRescue Helpful Tips</p>

            <p>With current hardware prices and performance levels, building your own gaming PC remains one of the best ways to get maximum value. It’s also a rewarding experience that saves money and teaches valuable skills for future upgrades and troubleshooting.</p>

            <h2>Pros of Building Your Own PC</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Better performance per dollar spent</li>
                <li>Full customization and easy upgradability</li>
                <li>Learning experience and personal satisfaction</li>
                <li>Individual component warranties (often longer than prebuilt systems)</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>When to Buy Prebuilt Instead</h2>
            <p>If you value convenience, full-system warranty support, or simply don’t have time to research and assemble parts.</p>

            <h2>How RigRescue Can Help</h2>
            <p>Whether you need help choosing the right parts, full assembly with a detailed walkthrough, or just remote advice — we’re here to help in the Deltona / Volusia area or remotely.</p>

            <div class="text-center mt-12">
                <a href="/contact"
                   class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg font-medium">
                    Get Help Building Your Gaming PC
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
